OL,5,F````` LINARES SUPER TOURNAMENT ````````
OL,7, Garry Kasprov reigns supreme yet again 
OL,8, with another superb tournament         
OL,9, performance, winning with a clear point
OL,10, His only defeat was a loss to Ivanchuk 
OL,11, and in the last round he defeated      
OL,12, Kramnik, his nearest rival.            
OL,14, British No2 Mickey Adams turned in one 
OL,15, of his best tournament perfomances     
OL,16, ever, coming equal 3-4th. His only     
OL,17, defeat was to winner, Garry Kasparov.  
