OL,7,FAndrew BurnettGfrom Kirkcaldy with his 
OL,8,Gswashbuckling, aggressive play, was the
OL,9,Gwinner of the Glenrothes Premier,      
OL,10,Gplayed at theFLomond CentreGwith       
OL,11,Gsupport fromFBaird & Co and The Royal  
OL,12,FBank of Scotland,Gwith a perfect score 
OL,13,GofC15/15.                              
OL,15,GThe tournament is unique in the sense  
OL,16,Gthat it has adopted theF"Premier       
OL,17,FLeague"Gscoring system - you receive   
OL,18,C3ptsGfor a win,C1Gfor a draw - to      
OL,19, discourage draws.                      
