OL,5,G```FKASPAROV vs. KARPOVG`````````````` 
OL,7,FKasparov and KarpovGare set to play a  
OL,8,Gbest of 18-game match in Paris this    
OL,9,GOctober to reunify the world title,    
OL,10,Gaccording to French media reports.     
OL,12,GThe prize fund is reported to be about 
OL,13,F15m FF (#1.6m)Gwith the organisers     
OL,14,Gbilling the contest as "the last World 
OL,15,GChampionship match of the century".    
